505
00:43:21,360 --> 00:43:23,780
 Pitanje je krupno.

506
00:43:23,780 --> 00:43:26,220
 Mi znamo od davnine,

507
00:43:26,220 --> 00:43:29,380
 mislim, to je staro pitanje,

508
00:43:29,380 --> 00:43:31,900
