533
00:44:12,180 --> 00:44:13,560
 Ili da ne prihvatim sebe

534
00:44:13,560 --> 00:44:15,020
 u svom spolu,

535
00:44:15,020 --> 00:44:16,580
 ili da ne prihvatim sebe

