00:44:16,580 --> 00:44:17,400
 u svom jeziku,

537
00:44:17,400 --> 00:44:18,080
 u narodu,

538
00:44:18,080 --> 00:44:18,840
 u obitelji.

539
00:44:18,840 --> 00:44:19,100
 Dakle,

540
00:44:19,100 --> 00:44:21,340
